videos.headline: Stoops is proud of how clean the Wildcats played
videos.description: No. 16 Kentucky's Mark Stoops is confident the Wildcats proved they are limiting turnovers and capable of playing a complete game.

videos.headline: UK QB Levis says Wildcats have a one-game mentality
videos.description: Will Levis feels No. 16 Kentucky's win over LSU was its most complete offensive game thus far and says the Wildcats are ready for the next game.
